{"tid":1497271,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港大學回應傳媒查詢罷課事宜：教與學將如常進行","createTime":"2019-08-23T01:40:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T02:23:47.000Z","uid":12108,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f775b6b9c85c4d5c65ac331a840af0f549b58d9a","tid":1497271,"uid":12108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T01:40:16.000Z","msg":"香港大學22日在其官網回應傳媒查詢罷課事宜時表示，新學年的教與學活動將會如常進行。<br />\n<br />\n  港大發言人指出，&ldquo;大學是學術教育機構，港大新學年的教與學活動將會如常進行。同學有表達意見的自由，而參與罷課的學生應留意這對他們的學習進度可能造成的影響，同時必須尊重其他人上課學習的權利。大學會密切審視有關狀況，以確保正常的教與學活動不受影響。&rdquo;"},{"pid":"119b22d8cd97d37350c30e48e780be6639013a95","tid":1497271,"uid":281926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T02:07:14.000Z","msg":"各位巴打絲打，頂住呀！<br />\n路還很長，記住齊上齊落！<br />\n香港人可攻可守，智勇雙全！<br />\n記住<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>永不分化！不割蓆！不篤灰！</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>It&rsquo;s now or never</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">824 機場復活，WE WANT YOU！而家搭車犯法呀？</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K9EGvnL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK9EGvnL.jpg&h=9da42bc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WKSEg2M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWKSEg2M.jpg&h=20a2e6bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/now5W2M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnow5W2M.jpg&h=db034c66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rC19Ef7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrC19Ef7.jpg&h=5ab15f09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KUdLW2O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKUdLW2O.jpg&h=132e85dd&s=